# docdb-split-conjunctive-bson-filter

## Description

Migrated to a declarative `.rra` rule with a precondition (RFC 0090 Phase 2).

## Rewrite

lhs: (filter (and ?p1 ?p2) ?input)
rhs: (filter ?p1 (filter ?p2 ?input))
when: is_bson_operator_filter("?p1")
